{"tid":648910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收何志平錢　烏干達基金曝光","createTime":"2018-05-01T06:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T09:07:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"63ee7f2453550079ff6671e43ba4e669d0c45b9f","tid":648910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377946?_ga=2.44756900.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377946%3F_ga%3D2.44756900.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=hUgXkzpu5NMhDT%2Frcyqzthv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=18d243f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377946%3F_ga%3D2.44756900.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=8b5a8dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377946?_ga=2.44756900.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月01日 <br />\n<br />\n收何志平錢　烏干達基金曝光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=e7aefb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事基金地址位於烏干達首都坎帕拉一商廈，樓下有賭場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【何志平涉賄】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉賄被捕的民政事務局前局長何志平再申請保釋，並披露與烏干達外長庫泰薩夫婦的電郵，間接令收「捐款」機構資料曝光。《蘋果》發現該個被視作掩飾受賄的機構，既無辦事處和電話號碼，連電郵網域都是在收款後才註冊，並在去年棄用；收到50萬美元捐款以來，網上沒任何基金工作資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地址為律師樓<br />\n<br />\n根據庫泰薩夫人Edith Kutesa電郵，收捐款的機構是「食物安全及可持續能源基金」，Edith在2016年2月底主動電郵聯絡何志平，提醒對方有關支持其基金的承諾，並附上該基金銀行戶口資料。何志平一方在5月將50萬美元匯至基金戶口，不過庫泰薩在近6個月後才以基金名義發感謝信，再將發信日期追溯至6月10日；信上有基金位於烏干達首都坎帕拉的地址、電話等資料。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局在起訴書提到該基金在2015年7月已註冊，但局方在2017年11月派員到場視察，該大樓並無任何屬於該基金的標示，大廈保安亦稱從未聽聞。記者根據信上資料，發現基金地址實為律師樓Capital Partners&amp; Advocates，庫泰薩曾是合夥人。至於基金兩個聯絡電話，一個屬於上述律師樓，另一個則屬於Edith的私人電子支付公司MCash。<br />\n<br />\n至於信上的電郵網域的註冊日正是2016年6月10日，與感謝信上日期相同，亦即收到捐款後才註冊。網域在1年後到期，但基金未續期，現轉手至一間餐飲公司。基金稱實行多個可持續發展目標，並為青年提供就業，但基金無網站，網上至今未見工作資料。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林偉聰  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n英男爵轟政府未對港人負責<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n土地大辯論花841萬請顧問"},{"pid":"479a00951827df938743f41c67e1083a013edaba","tid":648910,"uid":52595,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"107fd2c1174bdf8822db23b53b5da0468d7033a2","tid":648910,"uid":93986,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"Ukanda forever"},{"pid":"58dc76390b8ee100aabfe34879ed48bda90be475","tid":648910,"uid":54626,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"wakanda forever"},{"pid":"10cfbbd38b74efe8c1e3f1272f960bb79e570a10","tid":648910,"uid":13663,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/cf097b1d135d79540057d8a1c0985a98/tenor.gif?itemid=11141549\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fcf097b1d135d79540057d8a1c0985a98%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D11141549&h=777714f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6831613a23a43387e99493efb29a737c3a9a601c","tid":648910,"uid":16792,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Wakanda Forever</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e3325cc5ecd170bd11359d49980b05bfd7c4813a","tid":648910,"uid":22967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"樓上好齊心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6d98eb5affb474b94625a971aa376e79516989","tid":648910,"uid":16792,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e33